rows.label: qev092807_MSG0010
rows.name: —A few days later—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092807_MSG0020
rows.name: Thanks for coming.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092807_MSG0030
rows.name: Behold—the final product.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092807_JNK0040
rows.name: Praise

rows.label: qev092807_SEL0050
rows.name:
Remark that it feels like it could
take off at any second.

rows.label: qev092807_MSG0060
rows.name:
I'm taking a test flight with it later.
You should give it a spin too.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092807_JNK0070
rows.name: Question

rows.label: qev092807_SEL0080
rows.name:
Express your doubts about
whether it can really transform.

rows.label: qev092807_MSG0090
rows.name:
It's different from Skell vehicle mode.
You're in for quite a surprise![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092807_MSG0100
rows.name: Oh, also...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092807_MSG0110
rows.name:
Alicia and I—
henceforth we no longer work for Grenada.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092807_MSG0120
rows.name:
Alicia took full responsibility.
The top brass struck a deal with her regarding Kelemen's case.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092807_MSG0130
rows.name:
But hey, we finished everything we set out to do.
It felt like the perfect time to get out.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092807_MSG0140
rows.name:
That's right. Liesel and I were talking it through,
and we've decided to start our own company.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092807_MSG0150
rows.name:
Trust me, we'll do our darndest to
make our mark—we wanna be top dogs![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092807_MSG0160
rows.name:
We'll do it the right way this time,
keep things aboveboard.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092807_MSG0165
rows.name: We'll never stoop to Kelemen's level. Not ever.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092807_MSG0170
rows.name: All right, time for a ride.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092807_MSG0180
rows.name: This one's for our new venture![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092807_MSG0185
rows.name: And for good luck, too.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092807_MSG0190
rows.name: Of course. See you soon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092807_MSG0200
rows.name:
Go and stretch your wings—
Hraesvelg is feeling restless, I bet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092807_MSG0210
rows.name: And you—stick around, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092807_MSG0220
rows.name: You've seen Hraesvelg fight before...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092807_MSG0225
rows.name: Now watch him fly![ST:wait ]
